Today’s (THU) hours:
⏱12-4p TO-GO sales only 
⏱4-10p Tasting Room opens with normal service. Stoked to have back @lovehourlosangeles and their 🍔♥️💛 

Adding one more beer as we wind into the holiday weekend:

WEST COAST HEAVEN 💙 
Unfiltered West Coast/California Hazy IPA showcasing Motueka hops from New Zealand. Fermented with a clean and neutral yeast strain to allow the hops to take center stage. Unfiltered for a softer mouthfeel with a balanced bitterness. 7.1% ABV

🏖 HOLIDAY HOURS:
Sunday open 11-4p TO-GO ONLY

🚚 CA shipping available.

Two single-hopped classics return to our menu today. 

GLAMORO ✨ 
Double Dry Hopped (DDH) Double IPA featuring CITRA! (Formerly “Glamour Glitters, and Gold”) 8.3% ABV

SPOCK IT 🖖🏽
IPA showcasing GALAXY hops 6.8% ABV. A spacey crusher while orbiting around space. 

⏱ Open 12-7p TO-GO only (curbside and walkups)
🚚 CA shipping available.
